---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About PawDore"
  description="Learn about PawDore and our mission to help dog owners find the best products for their furry friends."
>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="post-content">
      <h1>About PawDore</h1>

      <p>
        PawDore was created with one simple goal: to help dog owners make better product decisions.
        With thousands of dog products on the market — from harnesses and beds to food and supplements —
        it can be overwhelming to figure out what's actually worth your money.
      </p>

      <p>
        That's where we come in. We spend hours researching, comparing specifications, reading veterinary
        guidance, and analyzing real customer experiences so you don't have to. Every recommendation on
        PawDore is backed by thorough research and a genuine desire to help your dog live their best life.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Review Products</h2>

      <p>
        Our review process involves researching product specifications and materials,
        analyzing hundreds of real customer reviews across multiple retailers,
        consulting veterinary resources and expert opinions,
        comparing products head-to-head on features, durability, and value, and
        regularly updating our guides as new products hit the market.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Promise</h2>

      <p>
        We'll always be upfront about our affiliate relationships. When you buy through our links,
        we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep PawDore running
        and continue producing free, helpful content. We never let affiliate partnerships influence
        our recommendations — if a product isn't good enough for our own dogs, we won't recommend it to yours.
      </p>

      <p>
        Have a question or suggestion? We'd love to hear from you at
        <strong>hello@pawdore.com</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
